      <span itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Person">
        <a title="Eric Bjerke" class="user" itemprop="url" name="Eric Bjerke" href="/user/show/924622-eric-bjerke">Eric Bjerke</a>
      </span>

        rated it
        <span class=" staticStars notranslate" title="really liked it"><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10">really liked it</span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p0"></span></span>



        

          <div class="uitext greyText bookshelves">
            Shelves:
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/924622-eric-bjerke?shelf=historical-fiction">historical-fiction</a>
          </div>
    </div>


        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer23562615" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer16050852412284737">This helped me discover the joy of historical fiction. I really learned a lot about slavery and the civil war while enjoying good stories. I am glad I never saw the mini-series. </span>

          </span>
        </div>


